Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:37.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been doing this for the last two hours,\nbut it's not getting clean at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't let my mom see my apartment like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She might even figure out that I'm hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What can I do? What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I can borrow Yamazaki's room, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom, this is my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you read stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That would just result in a different kind\nof misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's here already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wh... Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mi... Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you memorized my family tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't have time to\ntalk about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\pos(148,181)}TATSUHIRO SATO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going to let your mom\nsee your apartment like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I was cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in my way, so you need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I might as well, since I'm supposed to\nbe your girlfriend today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, just put the trash in this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:49.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If this is just an act, why would she come into some\nguys room and start helping him clean up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE3DFE7&\shad0\bord1\c&HDA8B32&\fscx86.25\fscy92.5\frz354.608\pos(147,261)}Beautiful Girls Land
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you read stuff like this, huh, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my research material, for making a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to read it, I'm obligated to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're obligated, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:22.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, around what time is your\nmother going to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...\NWhen is she arriving anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, damn, is that Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do we do? It's not clean at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this,\nwe have to play our last chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to initiate\NMission: Toss Everything Up On My Bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:40.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, just throw everything on my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a second! I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Wait just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, I guess it looks all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just have to camouflage that with this blanket,\nand it's good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fnSegoe Print\c&H000000&\frz310.046\pos(109,152)}me up at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fnSegoe Print\c&H000000&\frz302.741\pos(105,231)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M... My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had no idea... I'm mean, yeah,\nyou're busy all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ya... Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I redid your business cards.\NI'll put them right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H... Hey, Yamazaki! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding!\NYou're misunderstanding this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then again, maybe it isn't a\nmisunderstanding after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to do it all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More importantly, Sato, did you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a fax from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Pick me up"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you received this fax yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:35.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to take everything that\NI don't want my mother to see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and leave it there for the time being!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:42.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I want to you to somehow clear a space big\nenough for three people to sit down, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Tatsuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M... Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're research materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you read stuff like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just wait right here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sato, can I throw this doll away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My mother is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna try to buy some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so while I'm doing that, I want you to clean up\nas big of an area as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:49.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna say hi to her real quick. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, last night I kind of started rearranging\nmy apartment so it's kinda messy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't really planning on seeing\nyour apartment anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a single guy's apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I expect there's no place\nto even step anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, if I see it, I'm gonna want\nto start cleaning it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you don't have to show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, I did all that for nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More importantly, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatsuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's in there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The girlfriend you were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to clean anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She said we're going to go have lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean I'm included too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Supposedly we're a couple, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, she's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's very nice to meet you!\NI'm Misaki Nakahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:38.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you, Tatsuhiro!\NShe's almost too good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Tatsuhiro's mother, Shizue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's wonderful to meet you, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think about this place?\NI think the price is reasonable too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks like a nice restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see that they let you pick three\nthings for your lunch combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I brought the business cards that\NYamazaki made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:14.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The company's phone number is actually\NYamazaki's home number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, even if Mom calls the number,\NI'm sure Yamazaki will lie for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:26.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Y.S. Company,\nsoon to make its mark in the business world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I should be able to take care of the rest\nas long as she doesn't mess anything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H0091F9&\3c&H00093A&\bord3\shad0\fscx482.5\fscy457.5\move(104,70,242,70))}CHINATOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H0B76B7&\3c&H011B4C&\bord1.3\shad0\move(191,137,191,120)\fscx65\fscy71.25\t(\fscx50\fscy56.25)}CHINATOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was right to let Misaki pick the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like that at all.\NI just looked it up in the guidebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:18.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, I can't believe a cute girl like her\nwill be my daughter-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean '"your daughter-in-law"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:27.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I thought you two were dating with the intention\nof getting married in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Th... That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two aren't lying about this\nby any chance, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N... Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We wouldn't mind getting married\ntomorrow if we had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, Misaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this means that you've seen the birth mark on\NTatsuhiro's back and everything then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me what you like about Tatsuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What made you decide that\nyou want to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:11.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, what made me decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:16.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato is cool and handsome.\NHe's got a good job, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He knows a lot about computers and stuff, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Also there are other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Tatsuhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At this rate, it's just the matter of time\nuntil she finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better shift the conversation to\nsomething more work-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:14:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8BFB3&\3c&HB88175&\shad0\fscx130\fscy127.5\frz317.512\frx28\fry50\move(272,116,253,122)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Y.S. Company,\nsoon to make its mark in the business world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dumbass! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think my mother will call over there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but please continue to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try to hurry it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H777875&\fnSegoe Print\shad0\bord0\fscx158.75\fscy148.75\frz9.783\pos(200,117)}Tatsuhiro Sato
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H777875&\fnSegoe Print\shad0\bord0\fscx87.5\fscy103.75\frz9.064\pos(225,170)}Y.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I've noticed that you don't call\NTatsuhiro by his first name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been calling him "Sato,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I wonder if that's just how it is\nwith young people these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or are you holding back because I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This whole thing is a lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:15:00.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,About you being his girlfriend and his company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am his girlfriend, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, about his company, actually he's\nwriting scripts for them, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:18.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because I lived with him for eighteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been going along with this little play\nbecause he asked you to, right, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But look at how he's acting after all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can tell he's been frustrated the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:36.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet he can't stand the fact that he's been lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:42.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Though one might not expect it of him, he's had\na strong sense of justice since he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:50.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm envious of Sato for having\nsuch a nice mother like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tat-chan! Tell me, was it really\nyou who broke it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I was in elementary school, I'd often make\nmischief and get yelled at by Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:22.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, even back then I'd blame things on others\nand make all kinds of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My son didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That moment, my entire body froze up from guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't tell her the truth until\nafter that guy left my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But even so, she was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to go apologize to him together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:52.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At that moment, I promised myself that\NI'd never lie to my mom again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My, I'm so stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got to talk to Misaki today too,\nso I'm pretty content!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:15.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, Mom? I, err, to tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, I guess a mean ol' mother-in-law\nshould leave you two alone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to meet my friends after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:32.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the biggest knucklehead,\nbut please take care of him for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:38.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you guys came all the way out here,\nwhy don't you have a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro, hang in there, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you later, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, "hang in there" my ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is pathetic! The play is over!\NI'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna do as your mother told us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go talk a walk around here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we do that, I think positive things\nwill come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your mother is great, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think she's just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Normal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't even reach the normal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's actually, surprisingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't hang all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,People might be watching, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this a place where people on dates hang out?\NWhen did we get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In this place, we look more normal if we do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you think we're heading\nin the wrong direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at what they're doing in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sa... Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lipstick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did she do that for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They look so soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How much longer are you gonna\nmake me wait, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been two hours since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to the phone call\nfrom your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been standing by without even going to the\nconvenience store! Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry! Things happened and\nthe plan got canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, but I'll explain the details\nwhen I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H664D48&\3c&H271102&\shad0\frz313.973\frx32\fry54\pos(265,118)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not gonna fool me with these\nsweet buns, you know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My whole day was shot because of you, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh man, what a day...
